      "name": "Size-selector-open",
      "context": "expanded state, here we see the selected one still, but are now able to hover over the other sizes and click to select them. Upon clicking to select, the config collapses to the closed state but now depicting the new selected size. If the user clicks OUTSIDE of this open state without having selected a new size - the config collapses to initial closed state, and thus still depicting the original size.\n\n\n\nDont include this wrapper with the \"closed\" text, its just for the ai agent context. the actual state/layer is the \"Segment - Open\" inside here",
